at fir&s;t imagined this commendation was
ironical, but hearing it repeated again and again,
was filled with a&s;toni&s;hment at this &s;urpri&s;ing
change in the lieutenant's behaviours and after a
<PB N="49" REF="57">
long fit of mu&s;ing, concluded that Hatchway
