<HEAD>CHAP. VII.</HEAD>
<HEAD TYPE="sub">Divers &s;tratagems are invented and put in practice,
in order to overcome the ob&s;tina$y of <HI>Trunnion,</HI>
who at length is teized and tortured into the neo&s;e
