<P>THIS abrupt departure and unkind declara|tion
affected Mrs. Grizzle &s;o much, that
&s;he &s;ell &s;ick of &s;orrow and mortification; and after
having confined her&s;elf to her bed for three days,
&s;ent for her brother, told him &s;he perceived her
