affection. Her brother, though he did not muc$
$eli&s;h this te&s;timony of her love, neverthele&s;s th$$
&s;ame evening gave an account of this particular
<PB N="51" REF="59">
to Mr. Hatchway, who was al&s;o, as Mr. Pickle
