the terror of which was increa&s;ed by the &s;ilencc
and darkne&s;s of the night, as well as the eccho of
the pa&s;&s;age through which it was conveyed, n$
&s;ooner reached the ears of the a&s;toni&s;hed commo|dore,
than turning his eye towards the place from
whence this &s;olemn addre&s;s &s;eemed to proceed,
