<P>This important article being di&s;cu&s;&s;ed, Mr.
Hatchway &s;et out in the morning to vi&s;it the de|&s;pairing
&s;hepherde&s;s, and was hand&s;omely re|warded
for the enlivening tidings with which he
ble&s;&s;ed her ears. Sick as &s;he was, &s;he could not
