<P>In the afternoon the commodore &s;uffered
him&s;elf to be conveyed to her apartment, like a
$elon to execution, and was received by her in a
langui&s;hing manner and genteel di&s;habille, ac|companied
by her &s;i&s;ter-in law; who was, for
very obvious rea&s;ons, extremely &s;ollicitous about
