reply to her in&s;inuations, but with a mo&s;t vinegar
a&s;pect crawled out of his ne&s;t, and betook him|&s;elf
to re&s;t in another apartment, while his irri|tated
&s;pou&s;e di&s;mi&s;&s;ed the lieutenant, and from
the wreck of the hammock made an occa&s;ional
b$d for her&s;elf on the floor, fully determined to
