<HEAD>CHAP. X.</HEAD>
<HEAD TYPE="sub">The commodore being in &s;ome ca&s;es re&s;tif, his lady
has recour&s;e to artifice in the e&s;tabli&s;hment of her
throne; &s;he exhibits &s;ymptoms of pregnancy, to
