and candidly impart the motives that induced him
to leave her.</P>
<P>He accordingly repaired to her mother's hou&s;e
with a heavy heart, being attended to the gate
by Hatchway, who did not choo&s;e to leave him
alone; and being admitted, found Emilia ju&s;t
ri&s;en, and in his opinion, more beautiful than
