<LETTER>
<OPENER>Divine empre&s;s of my &s;oul!</OPENER>
<P>IF the refulgent flames of your beauty had not
evaporated the particles of my tran&s;ported
brain, and &s;corched my intellects into a cinder
of &s;tolidity, perhaps the re&s;plendency of my pa&s;|&s;ion
